34188310846, \"rank\": 0.03645908717652252, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McIlroy\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"his decision\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 604}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 657}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 684}, {\"ngram\": \"his amateur career\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before turning professional, McIlroy played for Ireland and the four-time major winner says he had no reason to change for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 769, \"end\": 776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8531401683544441, \"rank\": 0.1688035168115915, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McIlroy\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"the four-time major winner\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngram\": \"no reason\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an agreement between the Olympic Federation of Ireland and the British Olympic Association, athletes are permitted to choose which team they wish to represent.\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 925, \"end\": 952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an agreement\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 874}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Federation\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"Ireland\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"which team\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 997}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking in an interview withThe Guardianearlier this month, McIlroy explained why he decided to represent Ireland.\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1130, \"end\": 1137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8531401683544441, \"rank\": 0.1688035168115915, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"Guardianearlier\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1071}, {\"ngram\": \"McIlroy\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1091}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I had a sense of resentment towards the Olympics because I had always tried to stay so neutral and it presented me with this option of; what are you going to do?'\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"resentment\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1189}, {\"ngram\": \"this option\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McIlroy said.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McIlroy\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I had to get over that.\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All of my amateur career I played for Ireland.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1382, \"end\": 1389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8531401683544441, \"rank\": 0.1688035168115915, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my amateur career\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was very proud to play for Ireland.\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8531401683544441, \"rank\": 0.1688035168115915, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So why would I do anything differently as a professional?\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Tokyo felt like a throwback to the amateur days.\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1489, \"end\": 1494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.998843363245579, \"rank\": 0.001157187545960065, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a throwback\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"the amateur days\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All the federations were there.\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All the federations\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seeing people from the amateur game who I had not seen for decades.\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"the amateur game\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I really enjoyed the experience and I am sure Paris will be even better because I will get to go to some of the other events.\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1684, \"end\": 1689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997116902, \"rank\": 2.8840039655604994e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1669}, {\"ngram\": \"the other events\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's a bit like the Ryder Cup, I made comments before I had experienced it.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Ryder Cup\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"comments\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am excited to go back.'\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking more about his decision in 2021, McIlroy said: 'I made it more difficult for myself than I needed to.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his decision\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"McIlroy\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'My feeling towards it was more 'What will other people think?'\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2044, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My feeling\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"other people\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once I got that out of my head and just tried to do what was right for me, then it became easy.\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was me wrestling with all of those things.\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2186, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those things\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'As I said, previously, once I left trying not to upset anyone aside, then it was actually a pretty easy decision.\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2250}, {\"ngram\": \"a pretty easy decision\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision was I am going to play golf for the country or the nation that I have always played for through my junior and amateur days and now into the professional game.\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The decision\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2343}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2359}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"my junior and amateur days\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2438}, {\"ngram\": \"the professional game\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Even though the Olympics has given me this choice, there really wasn't a choice because all I have done throughout my life is play golf for Ireland so why would that change just because the tournament has changed.\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2617, \"end\": 2624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8531401683544441, \"rank\": 0.1688035168115915, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland_national_f